thread.title: Freshman Saffle offers depth on Cal’s defensive line
thread.title_full: Freshman Saffle offers depth on Cal’s defensive line - San Francisco Chronicle

author: Connor Letourneau
title: Freshman Saffle offers depth on Cal’s defensive line
text:
Photo: Al Sermeno / David Bernal, Golden Bear Sports Defensive end Cameron Saffle made his college debut Oct. 10 at Utah after missing Cal's first five games with a torn ACL. 2015 Washington State Cougars at Cal Bears Football. Cal wins 34-28. Defensive end Cameron Saffle made his college debut Oct. 10 at Utah...
The uniqueness of his circumstances have yet to dawn on Cameron Saffle. Fresh off his first college appearance, the Cal defensive end has little mental bandwidth for reflection.
